model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a local model where user details can be stored. The class stores the user's id, name, username, location, description, profile picture url, the venues where the user checked in, any other users they came in contact with and a list of keyword they used.
    Author:
    tudorsirbu
